# [EN] This file prevents temporary and generated files from being tracked by Git.
# [ZH] 此文件用于阻止 Git 追踪临时和自动生成的文件。

/[尝]库/
/[Ll]ibrary/
/[Tt]emp/
/[Obj]/
/[Build]/
/[Builds]/
/[Logs]/
/[UserSettings]/
/[MemoryCaptures]/

# [EN] Avoid tracking asset pipeline output
# [ZH] 避免追踪资源流水线输出
/[Aa]sset[Pp]ipeline/

# [EN] Memory dumps
# [ZH] 内存转储文件
*.clog
*.pvr

# [EN] IDE / VS Code / Visual Studio individual settings
# [ZH] 集成开发环境自动生成的解决方案和配置文件
.vs/
.vscode/
*.csproj
*.sln
*.suo
*.user
*.userprefs
*.pidb
*.booproj
*.svclog
*.shaderdump

# [EN] OS generated files
# [ZH] 操作系统生成的缓存文件
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db